revised_prompt: Visualize an enchanting Japanese garden filled with tranquility and beauty. Let it be crafted carefully wherein varied elements of nature harmoniously coexist. Stay true to traditional aesthetics, picturing a large pond filled with koi fish swimming gently, edged with smooth pebbles. Beside it, a red, arched wooden bridge crosses over the waters leading to a tea house hidden among bamboo trees. Next to these, a dominating cherry blossom tree stands, shedding its delicate pink petals on a Zen rock garden enclosed with neatly trimmed shrubs. Finish it with stone lanterns emitting a soft glow under the pale twilight sky.
